sections.heading: Money, defined.The term money includes all kinds of coin and all kinds of paper, issued by or under authority of the United States, circulating as money
sections.text: Money does not include central bank digital currency.SourceLaws 1903, c. 73, ยง 4, p. 389;R.S.1913, ยง 6292;Laws 1921, c. 133, art. I, ยง 5, p. 545;C
